---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contacto">
  <main class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen py-12">
    <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">Contacto</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 text-center max-w-xl">
      Â¿Tienes dudas, sugerencias o comentarios? Completa el siguiente formulario y nos pondremos en contacto contigo.
    </p>
    <form class="bg-navi  backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-8 w-full max-w-md flex flex-col gap-4">
      <label class="form-label" for="name">Nombre</label>
      <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required class="form-input" />

      <label class="form-label" for="email">Email</label>
      <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required class="form-input" />

      <label class="form-label" for="message">Mensaje</label>
      <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required class="form-input"></textarea>

      <button type="submit" class="mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-Orange text-white rounded hover:bg-Orange/80 transition-colors">
        Enviar
      </button>
    </form>
    <a href="/" class="text-Orange hover:underline mt-8">Volver al inicio</a>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
